title: Fresh Tomato Soup with Crispy Cheese Toast - Food Wishes
description:
When you grow up eating a certain thing a certain way, it can be challenging to enjoy that certain thing in a new, and significantly different way, which used to be the case for me when it came to any non-creamy tomato soup. Until I discovered this one, and all that changed.
